snippet.title: Usurper: Soulbound - Co-op playthrough with devs
snippet.description:
Wish list on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1420510/Usurper_Soulbound


Watch our 3D artist, Corey, play through the first portions of the game with a buddy. Can they make it?
